author: Pedro Fequiere Buzzfeed Staff
title: Build A Suit And We'll Tell You Which President You'll Sleep With
text:
Build A Suit And We’ll Tell You Which President You’ll Sleep With You got: Barack Obama 
You’ll be doing the dirty deed with Barack! Joe Raedle / Getty Images You got: George W. Bush 
Looks like you’ll be getting down and dirty with George Dubya. Chip Somodevilla / Getty Images You got: Bill Clinton 
Hopefully he’ll play the sax, because you’ll be playing ~the sex~ with Billy C. Timothy A. Clary / AFP / Getty Images You got: John F. Kennedy 
Yep! You’ll be F’ing JFK. National Archives / Getty Images 
You’ll be hooking up with Honest Abe. This is fucking history!… Literally. Alexander Gardner / Getty Images 
It’ll be the greatest, hugest, best thing eva!… Just kidding, alternative facts. ¯\_(ツ)_/¯ Mario Tama / Getty Images You got: George Washington 
You got George Washington! Good job getting past first base with the first president of the United States. Hulton Archive / Getty Images You got: Franklin D. Roosevelt 
You got Franklin D. Roosevelt! Emphasis on the D. Hulton Archive / Getty Images You got: Theodore Roosevelt 
You got Teddy Roosevelt! So it’s only right that you turn on some Teddy Pendergrass to set the mood. Hulton Archive / Getty Images
